data.value: 领先的

data.name: After four years of stable MainNet operation, Neo is undergoing its biggest evolution as it migrates to N3 - the most powerful and feature rich version of the Neo blockchain to date.
data.value: 经过 4 年的稳定运行，Neo 即将迎来自主网启动以来最大规模的全新升级 -N3。N3 将会成为迄今为止，最强大，功能最丰富的 Neo 区块链版本。

data.name: As a founding member of the interoperability protocol alliance Poly Network, Neo makes cross-chain interaction as easy as a native transaction.
data.value: 作为互操作性协议 Poly Network 的创始成员之一，在 Neo 区块链上进行跨链操作的体验就如同原生链上交易一样便捷。

data.name: As with any new paradigm, blockchain development comes with a learning curve. Rather than introducing additional overhead, Neo helps developers by integrating seamlessly with the world's most widely used languages and tools.
data.value: 理解一种新的范式的总是伴随着陡峭的学习曲线，区块链开发亦不例外。为尽量避免这些无意义的学习负担，Neo 通过无缝整合全球的通用开发语言和工具，帮助开发者快速入门。

data.name: BEST IN CLASS
data.value: 行业领先的

data.name: Connected with an ever-growing list of other blockchains, applications on Neo are not limited to interacting with native assets or contracts, but can easily tap into resources from heterogenous networks.
data.value: 随着更多的区块链加入 Poly Network, Neo 区块链上的应用不仅能够与原生的资产和智能合约进行交互，同时能够与更多异构区块链进行原子性交互。

data.name: Neo also boasts many other powerful community-built SDKs, compilers, code examples, and resources for all supported languages, including C#, Python, TypeScript, Java, and Golang.
data.value: Neo 也不遗余力的推动大量由社区开发的优秀工具：SDKs、编译器、代码模版和其他各种开发者资源。目前支持的开发语言包括 C#、Python、TypeScript、Java 和 Golang。

data.name: Neo makes it easy for users to interact with the next generation of decentralized services.
data.value: 与下一代去中心化服务交互，比以往更自然。

data.name: Neo separates governance from utility with two tokens - NEO & GAS.
data.value: Neo 拥有两种分工明确的原生治理和燃料通证 - NEO 和 GAS.

data.name: Neo was the first truly immutable blockchain. With majority approval between consensus nodes required for each new block, transactions on Neo are given immediate, irrevocable finality as soon as they are added to the blockchain. Neo's high performance dBFT consensus mechanism sparked a growing trend of adoption for BFT-based mechanisms across the industry.
data.value: Neo 作为首个具有单区块终局性的区块链，每个区块的产生都需要大多数共识节点的许可，每笔交易都可立即获得不可逆的最终确认。Neo 高性能的 dBFT 共识机制已经逐渐成为行业标杆，越来越多的区块链正在采用基于 BFT 的底层共识机制。

data.name: Neo's fork-proof dBFT consensus makes it the most powerful settlement engine in the world.
data.value: Neo 采用的防分叉 dBFT 共识机制，让 Neo 区块链成为全球最强大的清算引擎。

data.name: Neo's goal has always been to be the most developer friendly platform.
data.value: Neo 致力于成为最开发者友好的区块链平台。

data.name: Neo's native name service provides domain-mapping for a number of record types. Powered by NFTs to enable open trading, NNS aliases can be used to replace public addresses, contract hashes, and NeoFS containers with human-friendly names.
data.value: N3 中集成的原生域名服务提供多种类型的域名映射，为公钥、合约哈希或者 NeoFS 容器提供更便于理解和记忆的域名。同时，这些 NNS 域名本身是一种 NFT, 用户可以在公开市场进行自由交易。

data.name: Not looking to integrate, but want to participate? Earn GAS for leasing your unused storage.
data.value: 无集成需求，如何参与？- 出租你的储存空间获得 GAS.

data.name: Smart contracts are a revolutionary tool, but their usefulness is naturally limited by the data they can access. The native oracle service introduced in N3 allows developers to access rich off-chain data sources through HTTPS or NeoFS requests, opening up new opportunities to create valuable decentralized services.
data.value: 智能合约是一个革命性工具，然而其可用性天生受限于可访问的数据源。N3 中集成的原生预言机允许开发者通过 HTTPS 或 NeoFS 请求访问丰富的链下数据源，极大拓展创造各种有价值的去中心化服务的可能性。

data.name: Through NeoID, you can customize the precise level of attribute verification needed to ensure your contract operates correctly. Ensure regulatory compliance, filter out bots, or leave the doors open to everyone. Through its open claim issuance and validation tools, users can remain in full control of their personal information.
data.value: 通过 Neo ID, 你可以准确定义你合约中所需的身份信息以保证合规性和过滤机器人，让每个真实用户都能无忧体验优秀的去中心化应用。通过使用 NeoID 提供的开放身份的发行和验证工具，保证用户可以对个人的隐私信息有最完整的控制。

data.value: 总供给量固定 1 亿个且不可分割，为 NEO 成为最稀缺的数字资产奠定了坚实的基础。

data.name: With Neo's native oracle service, it becomes trivial for developers to tap into any external resources.

data.name: YOU DIDN'T KNOW
data.value: 好得

data.name: You wouldn't use your Starbucks shares to buy a cup of coffee, so why spend your share of the blockchain on transaction fees? NEO tokens represents ownership of the network, while GAS is used to pay for all operations and services. NEO holders can participate in governance and receive distribution of GAS tokens to spend on the blockchain.
data.value: 你并不会用你的星巴克股份来购买一杯咖啡，同理，你也不会用区块链的“股份”来为了你的链上交易付费吧？ NEO 通证对应着 Neo 区块链所有权，而 GAS 是用来为各种操作和服务付费。NEO 通证的所有者可以通过持有和参与治理来获得 GAS 分配，并用 GAS 在链上进行操作。

data.name: Your data, always securely encrypted and available. Maintain full control over where it is placed and how it is accessed to deliver your users a first class experience.
data.value: 你的数据, 始终安全加密, 随时取用。数据存放何处如何访问，尽在你掌握之中。
